 Remarks:
      1. Taiwan, Hong Kong and Macao are not covered in the service area for    “domestic”. “Local” refers to Shanghai Municipality.
      2. In these Terms and Conditions, “Domestic Call”    includes local to local calls, local to domestic long distance calls,    domestic calls while on domestic roaming. Voice call charges do not cover    17909 and 11808, Family Long-distance calls, 800 Paid Toll Free calls and    calls to Voice Information Service. Voice calls are charged by the minute.
      3. Inclusive Mobile Data Usage is restricted to    Mainland China only, irrespective of the type of network access by 4G, 3G or    2G – and excluding WLAN (WiFi).
      4. Yearly payment of CNY 2028 is available for Basic Package 169. Monthly inclusive allowances remain unchanged.
      5. Yearly payment of CNY 2189 is available for Basic Package 199. Customers will enjoy pay 11 months to get 1 month service free. Monthly inclusive allowances remain unchanged.
      6. Yearly payment of CNY 2990 is available for Basic Package 299. Customers will enjoy pay 10 months to get 2 months services free. Monthly inclusive allowances remain unchanged.
      
      
